object.customQuery:
select distinct a.formnum as ISOFormNumber,'' as FormDetailNumber, 
b.policynumber as policynumber, b.policyversion as policyversion,a.DisplayDesc AS 
formDescription , a.systemid,a.name, a.Status
 from dbo.form_stg a,
 (select  basicpolicy.systemid,basicpolicy.policynumber, case when len(basicpolicy.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',basicpolicy.policyversion)
when len(basicpolicy.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',basicpolicy.policyversion)
else basicpolicy.policyversion end as policyversion , basicpolicy.SubTypeCd from dbo.basicpolicy_stg basicpolicy
where basicpolicy.cmmcontainer='Policy')b 
where b.systemid=a.systemid 
-- and a.CMMContainer='Policy'
limit 1000
